					<Description><![CDATA[Weekly trigger for incineration DES. Fires every 7 days (offset 6.5d so it runs after recyclingProcessingEvent). If WasteToBeBurned > burningThreshold_t and no combustion is in progress, starts the DES chain: WasteDrying → Gasification → SlagFormation.]]></Description>
					<X>60</X><Y>1230</Y>
					<Label><X>10</X><Y>0</Y></Label>
					<PublicFlag>false</PublicFlag>
