					<Description><![CDATA[True when this truck is transporting non-IS waste to Intermediate for incineration. Set by NonIS_Disposal dispatch; cleared in home entry after receiveLandfillWaste() is called.]]></Description>
					<X>60</X><Y>220</Y>
